{"type":null,"faqId":26107,"title":"系统休眠后，WLAN 是否会自动断开？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:-0.2951389in;margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:justify;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;keep-with-next.within-page:always;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p4{margin-bottom:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Book Antiqua;font-size:9pt;}\n.p5{margin-left:1.4409722in;margin-top:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:9pt;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.3048611in;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>平板 的 WLAN 连接策略默认为：在充电时，WLAN 会一直保持连接。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>如需使 WLAN 一直保持连接，请参考如下步骤：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1.  </span><a name=\"gen-id1.6.11.2.3.1.1\"></a><span>在主屏幕上点击“设置”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1.  </span><a name=\"gen-id1.6.11.2.3.2.1\"></a><a name=\"gen-id1.6.11.2.3.2.1\"></a><span>点击或滑动 “WLAN” 后的开关至 “</span><a name=\"gen-id1.6.11.2.3.2.1.2.1\"></a><a name=\"gen-id1.6.11.2.3.2.1.2.1\"></a><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=91062\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”，开启 WLAN。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1.  </span><a name=\"gen-id1.6.11.2.3.3.1\"></a><span>点击“高级设置”</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<a name=\"gen-id1.6.11.2.3.3.2\"><a name=\"figd0e1845\"><a name=\"gen-id1.6.11.2.3.3.2.1.1\"></a></a></a><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=91063\" style=\"width:2.6680555in;height:3.9395833in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1.  </span><a name=\"gen-id1.6.11.2.3.4.1\"></a><span>点击“在休眠状态下保持 WLAN 连接”，然后勾选“始终”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<a name=\"figd0e1858\"><a name=\"gen-id1.6.11.2.3.4.1.3.1\"></a></a><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=91064\" style=\"width:5.5291667in;height:3.9409723in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<a name=\"gen-id1.6.11.2.4\"></a><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=91065\" style=\"width:0.5in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<span>所有图片仅供参考，具体操作请以实际界面为准。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":170,"faqType":"网络与数据共享","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"427","faqTypeCode":"Tablet-Internet-Data-Sharing","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1432262701000,"seriesProductName":"T1-A21w","visitedTimes":11,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"系统休眠,休眠,wifi,wifi 断开,wifi 关闭,网断开","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}